Determined to return the videos to their rightful owner, Jenkinson's Boardwalk employee Dan Camano launched a Facebook appeal - and found them.

Mr Christini and his wife, whose infant daughters are now 20 and 22, now have an 11-year-old daughter as well.

The blast from the past took them completely offguard.

'At first, complete surprise, and then just gratitude,' Mr Christini told ABC News today of how he felt when he heard the news.

